<plot>Five guys meet once a week, with their kids, to bemoan the fact that being a 'stay at home father' whilst their wives go out to work isn't all it's cracked up to be. It's Christmas - frustrated, lost and confused this culturally mixed bunch of middle aged man decide to redress the balance of the sexes and go on a testosterone fueled adventure, kids in tow, behind their wives' backs. That was their first mistake.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?247429</url></doc>
